{% layout false %}
{%- comment -%}
  Baklib Brand Guidelines (visual system spec)

  This file is the Single Source of Truth for this theme's (wiki/help) brand visuals:
  - For developers: a visualized page showing the complete design tokens and component
    examples; CSS can be copied directly.
  - For the theme: all layout / templates / snippets / statics must strictly align with
    the brand definitions in this file when using colors, radius, sizing, and components.

  Architecture (consistent with the baklib_ai template):
    1. Static tokens (radius / size / border / depth / noise)
       -> src/stylesheets/application.css :root
    2. Runtime color mapping (daisyUI --color-* <- platform-injected --theme-color-*)
       -> layout/theme.liquid <head> <style>, enables real-time customization from admin
    3. Brand default palette (HEX / OKLCH)
       -> config/settings_schema.json recommendations.color_schemas.baklib
          (admin selects with one click)

  Notes:
  - This page inlines CSS variables under [data-theme="baklib"], so it always displays
    the brand defaults regardless of site-level color customization — useful for
    developer reference.
  - URL: /p/brand (static page route under the statics/ directory).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%} 1. Brand full defaults — reference only; not applied to any CSS directly {%- endcomment -%}
{%- capture brand_defaults_css -%}
/* Baklib brand defaults · developer reference only */
{
  name: "baklib";
  color-scheme: "light";

  --color-base-100: #f7f5f3;
  --color-base-200: oklch(95% 0.0081 61.42);
  --color-base-300: oklch(90% 0.0081 61.42);
  --color-base-content: oklch(40% 0.0081 61.42);

  --color-primary: #0f766e;
  --color-primary-content: #f7f5f3;
  --color-secondary: #c2410c;
  --color-secondary-content: oklch(73.92% 0.2135 50.94);
  --color-accent: #0f172a;
  --color-accent-content: oklch(98% 0.003 247.858);
  --color-neutral: oklch(90% 0.0081 61.42);
  --color-neutral-content: oklch(40% 0.0081 61.42);

  --color-info: oklch(80.39% 0.1148 241.68);
  --color-info-content: oklch(30.39% 0.1148 241.68);
  --color-success: #14b8a6;
  --color-success-content: oklch(23.92% 0.0901 136.87);
  --color-warning: #fdba74;
  --color-warning-content: oklch(43.92% 0.1085 80);
  --color-error: oklch(63% 0.237 25.331);
  --color-error-content: oklch(35.1% 0.1814 22.37);

  --radius-selector: 2rem;
  --radius-field: 0.5rem;
  --radius-box: 1rem;
  --size-selector: 0.25rem;
  --size-field: 0.25rem;
  --border: 2px;
  --depth: 1;
  --noise: 0;
}
{%- endcapture -%}

{%- comment -%} 2. Static tokens (not user-customizable) -> src/stylesheets/application.css :root {%- endcomment -%}
{%- capture brand_static_tokens_css -%}
/* src/stylesheets/application.css */
@plugin "daisyui" {
  themes: false;
  exclude: scrollbar, rootcolor;
  logs: false;
}

:root {
  --radius-selector: 2rem;
  --radius-field: 0.5rem;
  --radius-box: 1rem;
  --size-selector: 0.25rem;
  --size-field: 0.25rem;
  --border: 2px;
  --depth: 1;
  --noise: 0;
}
{%- endcapture -%}

{%- comment -%} 3. Runtime color mapping (real-time admin customization) -> layout/theme.liquid <head> {%- endcomment -%}
{%- capture brand_runtime_mapping_css -%}
{% comment %} layout/theme.liquid <head> {% endcomment %}
<style>
  :root {
    --color-base-100: hsl(var(--theme-color-base-100));
    --color-base-200: hsl(var(--theme-color-base-200));
    --color-base-300: hsl(var(--theme-color-base-300));
    --color-base-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-base-content));
    --color-primary: hsl(var(--theme-color-primary));
    --color-primary-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-primary-content));
    --color-secondary: hsl(var(--theme-color-secondary));
    --color-secondary-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-secondary-content));
    --color-accent: hsl(var(--theme-color-accent));
    --color-accent-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-accent-content));
    --color-neutral: hsl(var(--theme-color-neutral));
    --color-neutral-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-neutral-content));
    --color-info: hsl(var(--theme-color-info));
    --color-info-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-info-content));
    --color-success: hsl(var(--theme-color-success));
    --color-success-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-success-content));
    --color-warning: hsl(var(--theme-color-warning));
    --color-warning-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-warning-content));
    --color-error: hsl(var(--theme-color-error));
    --color-error-content: hsl(var(--theme-color-error-content));
  }

  :root:has(input.theme-controller[value=dark]:checked),
  [data-theme="dark"] {
    /* Same as above, with every var replaced by --theme-color-*-dark */
  }
</style>
{%- endcapture -%}

{%- comment -%} 4. Recommended palette (one-click admin selection) -> config/settings_schema.json {%- endcomment -%}
{%- capture brand_schema_json -%}
